  Direction to use: 
   Every time you open the extension you have do a calibration thing:
1. click on Peoples icon present in google meet
2. click on Chat/in-call messages icon in the meet
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This extension will calculate how many times a person in meet responds using chatbox and by then it will show frequencies of responses in a 'table' form.
  So help teachers to analyze things.
